{"tid":1839072,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」醫護罷工可能有用","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T10:16:11.000Z","uid":338188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e09e7800b8c569a3e4ac996bc72fee2cf9707913","tid":1839072,"uid":338188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"我明白大家好緊張醫護被傳染<br />\n覺得醫護俾政苦當condom<br />\n希望醫護罷工<br />\n但我有啲野想講<br />\n<br />\n宜家最主要問題係政苦唔封關<br />\n醫護罷工可能可以迫到政苦封關<br />\n而呢個都係大家最希望見到<br />\n但宜家大家都知政苦痴線<br />\n如果佢真係唔封會點<br />\n大家又有無諗過<br />\n生化武器就係香港周圍走<br />\n但無人理 <br />\n個後果係好嚴重<br />\n<br />\n我覺得會有更好既方法<br />\n就係醫護界以外既人<br />\n一齊罷左先<br />\n要政苦知或者世界睇到唔係醫護發悔氣唔做先<br />\n而係香港人睇唔過眼而作出既決定<br />\n然後穩定左疫情醫護先再罷<br />\n<br />\n因為真係無理由俾啲生化武器周街走<br />\n希望有人明白我講咩 <br />\n唔好只一直屌醫護點解唔立即罷<br />\n真係要諗長遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99283fa025018260ec0b37b120c97a461d07f33","tid":1839072,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"Yes ching"},{"pid":"62867fb469dff383fb557b0373532f0fb97f2e06","tid":1839072,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"Help push pls"},{"pid":"d098a205954bb974ce744dd0e5d4c1b59c1aeac2","tid":1839072,"uid":335008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:13:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4166350762f3a659b1866d2735bf8f92244dbcb","tid":1839072,"uid":338188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"8e8e078cf8af8613861a5edb97fa727d21d27bec","tid":1839072,"uid":338188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a97d1fd7f538194d380871a63debfffbedbb96fb","tid":1839072,"uid":338188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:14:30.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"e0d58c7cfee1556843f85fff460a2b61c4700737","tid":1839072,"uid":3381